data.description: LUXURY LIVING IN DESIRABLE STARKEY RANCH~ Beautifully designed Homes By WestBay Flamingo III floor plan is the only model built in Starkey Ranch. This well-designed & impeccably cared for home features 4 brs, 3 ba, 2 car + bonus room spanning 2574 sqft with spacious fenced yard situated close to Homestead Park & pool and biking distance to Starkey K8! You will admire effortless design throughout like a rich wood-look tile in all the main living areas on the 1st fl, custom lighting, ceiling fans in all rooms & a modern Sherwin Williams Agreeable Grey paint throughout. The stunning exterior elevation has impressive curb appeal thanks to the Stacked Stone detail to 2nd story, Barrel Tile Roof, accent corbels, paver walkway & driveway & attractive landscaping. A decorative etched glass front door w/ iron inlay plus side light greets guests as they enter the foyer. To the left is a full bath with tub/shower combo and a spacious secondary bedroom. Luxury & comfort blend seamlessly in this open floor plan. Exquisite detail hallmarks the chef’s kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances featuring 5 burner gas range, built in microwave, dishwasher & refrigerator, all of which stay with the home! A multitude of 42’ Maple wood custom cabinets & drawers in Sherwin Williams Satin Dove are complimented by crown molding, matte black hardware, complimentary stylish glass backsplash, trash cabinet pull-out, pot drawers and pantry. The enlarged island features quartz counters, 3 glass pendent lights, space for 3 bar stools & sink with Moen faucet. A designated dining room is anchored by an attractive chandelier and complimented by 3 box windows. The spacious and well-lit living Room is enhanced by 2 windows sliders to patio, can lights, ceiling fan and provides space to support any furniture configuration. The private first Floor Primary Bedroom provides ample space for design, 2 windows with view of backyard and ceiling fan. Escape to your luxurious primary ensuite with ceramic tile, quartz counters, dual sinks, custom cabinets & drawers, double walk in closets & upgraded walk-in shower with listello accent. Ascend to the 2nd story bonus room offering multi-purpose space. In this desirable 2nd story split floor plan, you will find 2 additional bedrooms, 2 w/ ceiling fans, and an additional bath with tub shower combo and Dual Sinks. Oversized laundry room is located on 1st floor with plenty of space to add storage. Large covered patio offers a shady space to relax. *Irrigation System* Hurricane Shutters * Tankless Gas hot water heater * Epoxy in garage* Award winning Starkey Ranch offers brand new K-8 Magnet Schools with themes of Fine Arts, Computer Science, & World Languages with a Community Library, Theater & Cultural Center; 3 community pools; 3 playgrounds; 3 dog parks; 20 mile trail system for walking & biking, a community center & garden; ongoing events for all ages; Starkey Ranch Publix, Restaurants; & shopping! Schedule your showing today!
